{"tid":2038993,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[落order?] 蓬佩奧 與 英國外相藍韜文 通電話","createTime":"2020-05-27T21:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T22:11:24.000Z","uid":89160,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"262a2b47e738b95b0603d238044d88e2225db752","tid":2038993,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T21:01:33.000Z","msg":"post 錯台重新 post 多次<br />\n<br />\nSecretary Pompeo<br />\n@SecPompeo<br />\nProductive call with UK Foreign Secretary @DominicRaab on Hong Kong. Beijing&rsquo;s efforts to undermine Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy cannot go unchallenged by the international community.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1265741691098738689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1265741691098738689&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32TcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=99b25fa5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1265741691098738689&h=142b3ad6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1265741691098738689</a>"},{"pid":"f5d66087e86dea0245c51d2db3a138718499f7c6","tid":2038993,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T21:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb7d13efa5058eb3b95251ccc555428938d4757","tid":2038993,"uid":52594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T21:06:31.000Z","msg":"迫9 UK做野⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明UK收緊錢"},{"pid":"76c6945f0efb06a442437d628d7f7263b5cf4e34","tid":2038993,"uid":270889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T21:09:54.000Z","msg":"美帝吹雞  盟友要揀邊企了"},{"pid":"a4dfbb302c357dd06da295731030a0772807050d","tid":2038993,"uid":267921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T21:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ba28a4e916c0970fb16e18d3ce519816f00bc9","tid":2038993,"uid":89160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T21:25:45.000Z","msg":"BNO 平權其實唔夠，香港需要英國認証聯合聲明被中方撕毀。<br />\n<br />\n英國幫香港簽既《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》保留聲明提出「倘其根據公約第㆒條規定的義務，與其根據憲章﹙特別是憲章第一、二及<br />\n七十三條﹚規定的義務有任何抵觸，則以憲章規定的義務為準。」所以《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》第一條「自決權」不適用於香港。<br />\n<br />\n但當香港再唔符合聯合國憲章第73條：「聯合國各會員會，於其所負有或擔承管理責任之領土，其人民尚未臻自治之充分程度者，承認以領土居民之福利為至上之原則，並接受在本憲章所建立之國際和平及安全制度下，以充量增進領土居民福利之義務為神聖之信託」，咁就有理由恢復《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》第一條「自決權」既規定。"},{"pid":"d07ea17fa927b186293deeb098dca64aeeb94689","tid":2038993,"uid":113183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T21:41:48.000Z","msg":"一晚太多消息<br />\n好刺激"},{"pid":"7c07a72d2d1753fcf25bef601a64976546e2bfa2","tid":2038993,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d07ea17fa927b186293deeb098dca64aeeb94689","tid":2038993,"uid":113183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T21:41:48.000Z","msg":"一晚太多消息<br />\n好刺激"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:07:37.000Z","msg":"Solomon had said the D-day is coming <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d1e35b6df79520f3700570cf26f781e53a06f2","tid":2038993,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d07ea17fa927b186293deeb098dca64aeeb94689","tid":2038993,"uid":113183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T21:41:48.000Z","msg":"一晚太多消息<br />\n好刺激"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:10:01.000Z","msg":"手足血與淚....<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nit's just beginning."},{"pid":"7638bcadfe17be61b3dd3ccc3a42d692d4dfd4a7","tid":2038993,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d1e35b6df79520f3700570cf26f781e53a06f2","tid":2038993,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d07ea17fa927b186293deeb098dca64aee